quran[89]{c,v,t}:
  43,1,"Haa, Miim"
  43,2,Mi woondirii Defere …ďanngunde nden
  43,3,"Men wa…óii nde janngeteende [e …óemngal] aarabu, belajo'o, on haqqilay"
  43,4,"Pellet, hinde woni ka Amen gaa, ka yumma Defte, toowunde, √Īe√Īaande"
  43,5,"E Men acciray jippinangol on jantoore nden, …óuurngal on, fii on wonii yim…ďe fantim…ďe"
  43,6,∆äuu…óii e Annabaa…ďe …ďe Men nuli e adinoo…ďe …ďen
  43,7,"Annabaajo araali e ma…ď…ďe, si wanaa …ďe jalkitay mo"
  43,8,Men halki ko …ďuri …ďe sa…ótude doole ! Toode mise adinoo…ďe …ďen yawtiino
  43,9,"Ko pellet, si a lamndike …ďe: \"Ko hommbo tagi kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin?\" ∆Āe wi'ay: \"Ko Foolu…óo, Anndu…óo On tagi …ói"
  43,10,"On wa…óiran…óo on leydi ndin weertaandi, O wa…óani on …óate e mayri, fii no …óoworon"
  43,11,"On jippinr…óo to…ďo ka kammuu, yeru haaju, Men wuurnitiri ngo leydi maayndi. Ko non yaltinirte…óon"
  43,12,"On tagu…óo nooneeji …óin fow, O wa…óirani on e laa…óe …óen e neemoraa…ói …óin, ko wa…ó…óoron"
  43,13,"fii yo on fotondir e hoore majji, refti annditon neema Joomi mon On, tuma fotondir…óon e majji, wi'on ontuma: \"Senayee woodanii eltan…óo men …óum On, men wonaano taaqanaa…ďe …óum"
  43,14,"menen non, ko ka Joomi amen woni ko men ruttotoo"
  43,15,"∆Āe wa…óani Mo ge…ďal e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen ! Pellet, on ne…ó…óanke ko yeddu…óo …ďanngu…óo"
  43,16,"Kaa woo O jogiti …ďi…ó…ďe rew…ďe e ko O tagi kon, O heertinani on …ďi…ó…ďe wor…ďe …ďen"
  43,17,"Si go…ó…óo e ma…ď…ďe wewliniraama ko o wa…óirani kon Hinaranke On misal, yeeso makko ngon ni…ď…ďita metteendi hombo suu…ói"
  43,18,"E ko on ne'etee…óo e cu…óaari, hara kanko on ka yeddondiral, wanaa o …ďannginoowo haala"
  43,19,"∆Āe wa…ói Malaa'ikaa…ďe taw…ďe …ďen ko jeyaa…ďe Jom Hinaranke On, rew…ďe ! Kere …ďe seedino tageede …ďen? Awa fii seedagol ma…ď…ďe ngol winndete, …ďe lamnditoyee"
  43,20,"∆Āe wi'iti: \"Si Jom Hinaranke On haajuno, men rewataano …ďe\". ∆Āe alanaa …óum hay e ganndal; …ďe wonaali, si wanaa hi…ďe fena"
  43,21,"Kaa ko Deftere Men addani …ďe ado ndee …óoo, hara ko nden woni ko …ďe jogitii"
  43,22,"Si ko woni, …ďe wi'iu: \"Menen men tawu baabiraa…ďe amen …ďen e diina, haray ko e batteeji ma…ď…ďe men feewirta"
  43,23,"Ko wano non, Men nulaali jertinoowo aditaade ma e saare woo, si wanaa hooree…ďe ma…ď…ďe neemii…ďe wi'ay: \"Menen men tawu baabiraa…ďe amen …ďen e diina, …óum non ko batteeji ma…ď…ďe …óin men √Īentinta"
  43,24,"O maaki: \"Hay si mi addan on ko …ďuri feewude kon ko tawru…óon baabiraa…ďe mon …ďen?\" ∆Āe wi'i: \"Menen dey, ko men yeddu…ďe ko nulida…óon e mun kon"
  43,25,Men yottii e ma…ď…ďe. ndaare no battande fennu…ďe …ďen wa'unoo
  43,26,"Janto tuma Ibraahiima maakannoo ben makko e yim…ďe makko …ďen: \"Min on ko mi da…óndii…óo e kon ko rewoton"
  43,27,"si wanaa On tagu…óo lam, Kanko On, O fewnay lam"
  43,28,"O wa…ói ngol konngol heddotoongol …ďaawo makko, belajo'o, …ďe ruttoto"
  43,29,"Si ko woni, Mi dakmitii …ďee …óoo e baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, haa nde goonga kan arunoo e ma…ď…ďe, e Nulaa…óo …ďanngu…óo"
  43,30,"Nde goonga kan arunoo e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe wi'i: \"∆äum ko mbilewu, menen ko men yeddu…ďe …óum"
  43,31,"∆Āe wi'iti: \"Ko hanno ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinee e gorko maw…óo ca'e …óen …ói…ói"
  43,32,"E ko kam…ďe senndata yurmeende Joomi maa nden? Awa ko Menen woni ko senndi nguureeji ma…ď…ďe …óin hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, ka nguurndam aduna. Men …ďamti yoga ma…ď…ďe e hoore …ďeya, darjaaji, fii no yoga ma…ď…ďe jogitora yoga eeltane. Haray ko yurmeende Joomi maa nden, …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e kon ko …ďe moo…ďata"
  43,33,"Si wanaano fii wata yim…ďe …ďen wonu mofte goote, Men wa…óayno e cuu…ói kala yeddu…óo Hinnaranke On: ki…ď…ďe kaalisi e Ňčabbir…óe ka …ďe ∆īawra"
  43,34,"(Men wa…óayno kadi) e cuu…ói ma…ď…ďe …óin, dame e nda…ó…óude ka …ďe so…ď…ďindoo"
  43,35,"e cu…óaari. Kono …óum fow wonaali, si wanaa dakamme nguurndam aduna. Ko laakara on ka Joomi maa, woni fii gom…óum…ďe …ďen"
  43,36,"Kala …óuurnii…óo e jantoore Hinaranko On, Men wuurta mo e seytanuuru, hara ko ndun woni ko o coowodata"
  43,37,"∆äin (awaseeji) non, ko sakkoray…ói …ďe e peewal ngal, haa ka …ďe sikkata hi…ďe feewi"
  43,38,"Haa si o aroyii e Amen, o wi'a: \"Ee bone ! hara hakkunde am e maa wo…ó…óirayno go…ó…óal fu…ó…óir…óe …óen …ói…ói wo…ó…óiri ! A bonii cinndadii…óo"
  43,39,"[∆äum] nafataa on hannde - nde tawnoo on too√Īii - wonnde ko ka lepte hawtu…óon"
  43,40,E ko an naninta faa…óu…óo maa fewnaa bum…óo e on won…óo e nder majjere …ďanngunde
  43,41,"Si Men aru ∆īettitude ma, haray ko Men yottotoo…ďe e ma…ď…ďe"
  43,42,"maa hara Men holle ko Men kammbirani …ďen kon, haray noon ko Men gaynoo…ďe fii ma…ď…ďe"
  43,43,"Jogito kon ko wahayinaa e maa…óa. Pellet, hi…óa jokki laawol focciingol"
  43,44,"Ndee non [Alqur'aanaare], ko nde teddungal maa an e yim…ďe maa …ďen. Aray nde lamndite…óon"
  43,45,"Lamndii e …ďen Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďe Men nulunoo ado maa, si Men wa…óuno ko wanaa Hinnaranke On, rewetee…ói goo"
  43,46,"Gom…óii Men immindinii Muusaa e Aayeeje Amen …óen, haa e Fir'awna e mbatu mun ngun, o maaki: \"Ko mi Nulaa…óo Jey…óo tagu ngun"
  43,47,"Nde o addannoo…ďe Aayeeje Amen …óen, e jaka yoo hi…ďe jala…ói"
  43,48,"Men hollaali …ďe Aaya, si wanaa haray on …ďuri adii…óo mo on mawnude. Men nanngiri …ďe lepte …óen, belajo'o, …ďe ruttoto"
  43,49,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Ko an yo mbileejo! Torano men Joomi maa, ko O ahodi kon e maa…óa. Pellet, ko men feewoo…ďe"
  43,50,"Nde Men huncannoo…ďe lepte …óen, e jaka yoo, hi…ďe firta [ahadi]"
  43,51,"Fir'awna noddi e yim…ďe …ďen, o wi'i: \"Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, wanaa min jey laamu Misra? E hino …óii can…ói no ila e ley ku…ďeeji am? E on yiyataa"
  43,52,Kaa mi …ďuraa teddude oo hoy…óo mo e…ď…ďataa la…ď…ďinnde haala
  43,53,"Awa ko hanno jawle kaŇčŇče werlee e makko? Maa…óum Malaa'ika'en arda e makko, na jokkondiri"
  43,54,"O …óaytini yim…ďe makko …ďen, …ďe …óowtii mo. Pellet, …ďen …óon laatino yim…ďe faasiqii…ďe"
  43,55,"Nde …ďe tikkinnoo Men, Men yottii e ma…ď…ďe; Men yooli …ďe fow"
  43,56,"Men wa…ói …ďe ardii…ďe e misal, wonannde sakkiitii…ďe …ďen"
  43,57,"Tuma nde ge…óal neene Maryama on piyiranoo misal, tawaa yoo, yim…ďe maa …ďen no soo∆īira …óum"
  43,58,"…ďe wi'i: \"Ko rewetee…ói amen …óin …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude, kaa ko kanko?\" ∆Āe piyiranaali ma ngal (misal), si wanaa fii wennjugol. Wurin, ko …ďe yim…ďe sa…ótu…ďe wennje"
  43,59,"Awa (Iisaa) wonaali, si wanaa jeyaa…óo mo Men neemini e mun, Men wa…ói mo misal woannde …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen"
  43,60,"Si Men haajuno, Men wa…ótitirayno on Malaa'ika, ko lomtoo ka leydi"
  43,61,"Pellet non, ko o anndinorde Darngal. Wata on sikkito fii maggal. Jokkee lam, ko …óum woni laawol focciingol ngol"
  43,62,"Wata seytaane falo on ! tawde pellet, ko o ga√Īo mon …ďanngu…óo"
  43,63,"Nde Iisaa ardunoo e …ďanngu…ói …óin, o maaki: \"Gom…óii mi ardanii on e √Īee√Īal, e no mi …ďannginirana on yoga e ko luutondir…óon e muu…óum. Haray hulee Allah, …óofto…óon mi"
  43,64,"Pellet, ko Alla Woni Joomi am e Joomi mon. Rewee Mo. Ko …óum woni laawol focciingol ngol"
  43,65,"Feddeeji …óin luutondiri hakkunde majji. Bone woodanii …ďen yeddu…ďe, immorde e lepte √Īalaande muusu…óe"
  43,66,"Hara …ďe habbi si wanaa nde Darngal ngal ardata …ďe e juhal, hara …ďe so'aa anndude"
  43,67,"Weldu…ďe …ďen, nden √Īalnde, yoga ma…ď…ďe ko ayroo…ďe yoga; si wanaa gom…óum…ďe …ďen"
  43,68,Ko onon yo jeyaa…ďe Am ! Kulol alanaa on hannde; wonaa on sunotoo…ďe kadi
  43,69,"…ďen gom…óim…ďe Aayeeje Amen …óen, …ďe woni jebbilii…ďe"
  43,70,"naatee ka Aljanna, onon e nanndu…ďe e mon, hi…óon sa…ónee"
  43,71,"[Golloo…ďe] hino wanngindinee e ma…ď…ďe, mirannji kaŇčŇče e √Īeddu…óe; hino ton kadi: kala ko wonkii muuyetee, gite dakmitoo. Hara le, ko on duumotoo…ďe ton"
  43,72,"Ko on woni Aljanna mo roninira…óon, sabu kon ko gollayno…óon"
  43,73,"Hino woodani on ton, muuyantee…ói …óuu…óu…ói, …ói √Īaamoton e mun"
  43,74,"Pellet, bom…ďe …ďen, ko ka lepte Jahannama …ďe luttoyta"
  43,75,"…ďe hoynantaake, tee hara ko …ďe ta∆īii…ďe ton"
  43,76,"Men too√Īaani …ďe few, si ko woni, ko kam…ďe woni too√Īu…ďe …ďen"
  43,77,"∆Āe nodda: \"Ko an yo Maaliku ! Yo Joomi maa gaynu fii amen !\" O wi'i: \"Pellet, ko on luttoo…ďe [ton]"
  43,78,"Gom…óii Men addanii on goonga kan ; kono …óuu…óu…ďe e mon, ko a√Īu…ďe goonga"
  43,79,Kaa …ďe e…ď…ďu feere ? Doo ko Men fewjoo…ďe
  43,80,Maa hara …ďe sikku Men nanataa gunndooji ma…ď…ďe e sirru ma…ď…ďe? Oo‚Äôowoye! Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďen hino maandina takko ma…ď…ďe
  43,81,"Maaku: \"Si Hinaranko On no jogitii …ďi…ó…óo, ko min adotonoo rewude on"
  43,82,"Senayee woodanii Jey…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, Jey…óo Arsi kin; laa…ďu…óo e kon ko …ďe sifrotta Mo. @Corrected"
  43,83,"Accu…ďe …ďe jumpa, …ďe fija haa …ďe hawroya e √Īalaande ma…ď…ďe nde…ďe fodaa"
  43,84,"Ko Kanko woni On rewetee…óo ka kammu e rewetee…óo ka leydi, ko Kanko kadi woni √Ďee√Īo, Anndu…óo On"
  43,85,"Barke heewanii On Mo woodani …óum, laamu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji. Ko ka Makko anndal fii Darngal woni. Ko ka Makko kadi ruttete…óon"
  43,86,"∆äi …ďe rewata …óin gaanin Makko jeyah tefoore, si wanaa seedii…ďe goonga …ďen, hara hi…ďe anndi"
  43,87,"Ko pellet, si a lamndike …ďe, ko hommbo woni ko tagi …ďe? ∆Āe wi'ay: \"Ko Allah\". Ko honno non …ďe yiiliraa"
  43,88,"[Himo anndi kadi] fii ko (Nulaa…óo) on maakunoo kon: \"Ko an yo Joomi, pellet, …ďee ko yim…ďe …ďe gom…óintaa"
  43,89,"Awa yaafo …ďe, maakaa: \"Kisal !\" Aray ndebe annda"